### Tool Instruction
POST http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma3:1b",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant. You have access to a tool called <tool>get-weather {city}</tool> that returns the current weather for a given city. Use it when the user asks about the weather. When the user asks about the weather in Vienna, send <tool>get-weather Vienna</tool> to get the weather information."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What's the weather in Vienna?"
    }
  ]
}
